%%{init: {'theme': 'base', 'themeVariables': { 'fontFamily': 'Microsoft YaHei' }}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 用户
    participant F as 前端工作台
    participant A as /api/sessions
    participant T as TeachingAssistantService
    participant P as LacquerTutorAgent
    participant L as LLM
    participant S as SessionStore

    U->>F: 从左侧切到模块
    F->>A: POST /api/sessions {scene_key, query, mode}
    A->>S: create session

    alt knowledge / learning / safety
        A->>T: create_artifact(scene_key, query)
        T->>L: grounded 生成 / refine
        T-->>A: ModuleArtifact
        A->>S: 保存状态与消息
        A-->>F: response.type = artifact
    else planning / troubleshooting
        A->>P: start_session(query)
        P->>L: intent / slot extraction / VoI scoring
        P-->>A: question 或 contract
        A->>S: 保存状态与消息
        A-->>F: response.type = question / contract
        opt 用户继续回答
            F->>A: POST /api/sessions/{id}/answer
            A->>P: submit_answer + advance
            P->>L: 继续追问或生成结果
            A->>S: 更新状态
            A-->>F: question / contract
        end
    end
